stories.title: 4th Match, West Indies v Pakistan, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1588th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: Poor batting lets down Pakistan
stories.summary:
Kingstown (St Vincent), April 13: Pakistan batting failed to come to
terms with the variable bounce of Arnos Vale pitch as it wilted and
doomed the tourists to their first defeat against the West Indies in
the triangular one-day series here on

stories.title: Adams' Boys Whip Pakistan In One-Sided Match
stories.summary:
Kingstown - It was supposed to have been a contest with the
competitiveness of a Lennox Lewis-Evander Holyfield bout

stories.title: West Indies v Pakistan Preview
stories.summary: The 4th Match of the tournament starts at the Volcanic Island of St Vincent amidst buzzing excitement of the islanders who have been keenly waiting for a contest between Pakistan and the West Indies
